::Hot Rod::

Hot Rod looked at Iron Rapter.
"I brought this bot(Silver Sting) here, from the forest, he want to
join. And what were you all talking about? Any mission, that you may
need my help on?" He said. He could tell the relationship between Prowl
and the commander. Prowl was a lucky bot.
